contents.desc: IT’S A…. Watch till the end.💙🩷
My husband and I were the ones to surprise our close friends and family with the gender of our little one…

We set up a fun Holiday themed game where everyone picked a gift box under the tree, each holding either a pink or blue ornament. One by one, our friends and family took turns opening their box and hanging their ornament on the correct tree.🎄
The catch? Both trees ended up with the same number of pink and blue ornaments, just as we planned. Then came the big moment…
We brought out a special box with a unique ornament revealing a picture of our baby inside… We then hung it on the correct tree finally revealing what little baby Weichers is…
It was so fun getting everyone involved and was such a special day I will cherish forever…💙
#genderreveal #boyorgirl #genderrevealparty #babyboy #babygirl #babyreveal #heorshe #fy #boymoms
